Fourth Department,

February, 1969

(February 13, 1969) The People of the State of New York ex rel. William A. Tarpley, Appellant v. Vincent R. Mancusi, as Warden of Attica Prison, Respondent.

Judgment unanimously affirmed. (See People ex rel. Thierry v. Glasser, 1 A D 2d 929.) (Appeal from judgment of Wyoming County Court, dismissing writ of habeas corpus, following a hearing.) Present—Goldman, P. J., Witmer, Gabrielli, Moule and Bastow, JJ.
